cs.CV, cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.MM, cs.AI. 

The paper deals with video captioning, which involves both computer vision and natural language processing. Therefore, cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) and cs.CL (Computation and Language) are the most likely categories. The paper also proposes a novel LSTM cell, which involves machine learning techniques, making cs.LG (Machine Learning) a likely category as well. Additionally, the paper evaluates its approach on large-scale datasets, which could fall under cs.MM (Multimedia) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence).
